Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:22.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Che alibi potrà fornire quella fotocamera?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.18,0:24:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Questa l'ho scattata io!
